survey_response.review_text: Dr. Vishwas is very friendly, transparent and practical. He listens to patients really well and takes time to explain the issues in detail and provides best solution to it. He doesn't exaggerate issues. He is very practical, he gives examples of his own experiences and make patients understand the issue in a better way. He neither prescribes unnecessary medicine nor recommend any outside products to babies. He takes time to councel parents on parenting tips in a friendly manner. I highly recommend Dr. Vishwas to everyone. The best pediatrician have ever met so far.
